# Prism Portfolio — Figma Sync

When the user asks to apply Figma changes to GitHub for `prism-portfolio`:

1. Read Figma file `izxX8YJ16HiW3JB4sQsClp` (Prism Theme variables + page frames)
2. Map Figma Variables (`Prism Theme` collection) → `design/tokens.json` color keys:
   - `color/bg` → `color.bg`
   - `color/bg-elevated` → `color.bgElevated`
   - `color/text` → `color.text`
   - `color/text-muted` → `color.textMuted`
   - `color/accent` → `color.accent`
   - `color/accent-hot` → `color.accentHot`
   - `color/accent-pink` → `color.accentPink`
3. Update `content/site.json` and `content/projects.json` if page text frames changed
4. Run `npm run apply:tokens` in `prism-portfolio/`
5. Commit/push only when the user explicitly asks

User phrase examples: "Figma 토큰 변경 GitHub에 적용해줘", "Figma에서 바꾼 디자인 prism-portfolio에 적용해줘"
